I have some of those Evercoat squares. They stick like bugs on the front of 
your bus, however they seem to dry out after a year or two and lose their 
effectiveness. Try the stuff from:

http://www.secondskinaudio.com/

The damplifier is good stuff, as is the Spectrum. All a bit pricey however. 
You might also check on this link:

http://www.thesamba.com/vw/forum/viewtopic.php?p=3242923#3242923


